Package boundary

Class StaffMainPage

java.lang.Object
boundary.StaffMainPage
Direct Known Subclasses:
ManagerMainPage
public class StaffMainPage extends Object
StaffMainPage class is used to display the main page for the staff to interact with the system. The staff can view new orders, view an order, update order status, change password, and log out.
